{"tid":952660,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"1877 君實生物","createTime":"2018-12-23T10:17:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-31T06:25:52.000Z","uid":52010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8a64b7e9b6dd72b9d18405c3d9c84a9233c0bb16","tid":952660,"uid":52010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T10:17:52.000Z","msg":"創新驅動型生物製藥公司君實生物（０１８７７）公布招股結果，公開發售部分錄得超額認購３﹒７９倍，申請一手至五手中籤率１００％，股份定價為１９﹒３８元，為招股價１９﹒３８元至２０﹒３８元之下限價。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n內地「新三板」上市的生物製藥公司上海君實生物醫藥科技(01877)將於下周一掛牌,於上市前夕,其暗盤價上升,一手最多賺3720元。<br />\n<br />\n據輝立交易場資料顯示,君實暗盤開市報20.5元,較招股價19.38元,升5.78%;之後高見23.45元,升21%,收報23.1元,升19.2%,每手1000股,不計手續費,一手賺3720元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n準備爆升<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c65e4bdcf9aae151af8b16ca2905a000c3c2823f","tid":952660,"uid":52010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T05:42:35.000Z","msg":"潛力股<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4810114743588432eff7d015d3d69870129f081","tid":952660,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T08:04:07.000Z","msg":"FAT FAT"},{"pid":"2905e91743cbf17fea3d6b28df9db38510e8dfb5","tid":952660,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T08:09:47.000Z","msg":"Hi同齡人<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dddf98387b735d5373fc4321c5e121d304feb36","tid":952660,"uid":52010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T06:25:52.000Z","msg":"2018收<br />\n<br />\n上海君實生物醫藥科技股份有限公司<br />\n1877   24.2&nbsp;HKD<br />\n<br />\n信達生物製藥<br />\n1801   24.1&nbsp;HKD<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}